{"tid":12040,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[Pop-Punk][alter-Rock][Power-Pop]Easy-Core] 傳教區","createTime":"2016-11-29T13:24:31.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T04:47:13.000Z","uid":12475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"645cb2b408ff923562a5805fdc94b6d554918a31","tid":12040,"uid":12475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T13:24:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://40.media.tumblr.com/e5633ce5599a486dd3e31c8986dc5a53/tumblr_inline_nrdxroT9VS1smue6i_1280.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F40.media.tumblr.com%2Fe5633ce5599a486dd3e31c8986dc5a53%2Ftumblr_inline_nrdxroT9VS1smue6i_1280.png&h=6d677e26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n入POP-PUNK我們信<br />\n<br />\npop punk一直係音樂界既gateway music,<br />\npop punk帶領好多原本只係聽billboard,聽youtube-pop 習慣被主流媒體feed既人進入主動搵歌聽既新世界!<br />\n好多人會係聽開punk pop之後,識左好多方法去搵自己真正喜歡,真正岩自己既音樂 <br />\n<br />\n所以我覺得我地有必要向大家推介POP PUNK<br />\n等更多人寧願接觸更多唔同既音樂<br />\n<br />\n我們既信念係:<br />\nUntil you checked out all types of Music,<br />\notherwise you can never say no to this song.<br />\n<br />\n我會做一個歌LIST叫做 傳教<br />\n入面放左少少標題所提及既類型既BAND類型,<br />\n希望各位巴打可以SHARE依條LINK,<br />\n同埋不斷向我提供更多既&quot; GATEWAY MUSIC&quot;<br />\n等更多人可以加入依個FAMILY<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL0Vl5lZhLFQWR3YdkzB_C0BxXPUt79W6q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fplaylist%3Flist%3DPL0Vl5lZhLFQWR3YdkzB_C0BxXPUt79W6q&d=TV1mljVccv2Dt1EdWC3TiUsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=4ec11575\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL0Vl5lZhLFQWR3YdkzB_C0BxXPUt79W6q</a>"},{"pid":"2b08032216856e241795b42d522e09dc03996242","tid":12040,"uid":12475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T13:27:44.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"8c614ee8741b7d0950484cfe011d077ef72f9ab0","tid":12040,"uid":12475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T13:30:01.000Z","msg":"同埸加映:<br />\n<br />\n【Indie】此時此刻，你在播放那一張專